code: /**  * Sets the durable subscription Id required for durable topics.  */ @Override public void setDurableSubscriptionId(String durableSubscriptionId) {     super.setDurableSubscriptionId(durableSubscriptionId).     subscriptionId = durableSubscriptionId.     durable = true. }

comment: /**  * Sets the subscription Id, required for durable or shared topics.  */
code: /**  * Sets the subscription Id, required for durable or shared topics.  */ public void setSubscriptionId(String subscriptionId) {     this.subscriptionId = subscriptionId. }
/**  * Sets topic consumer to durable.  */ public void setDurable(boolean durable) {     this.durable = durable. }
/**  * Sets the consumer to shared.  */ public void setShared(boolean shared) {     this.shared = shared. }
